# 鉴权矩阵（全角色）

{
  "noauth": {
    "/api/accounts": 401,
    "/api/v1/vm/cockpit": 401,
    "/api/detail": 401
  },
  "overall_login_err": null,
  "overall": {
    "/api/v1/vm/cockpit": 200,
    "/api/accounts": 401,
    "/api/detail": 401,
    "/api/settings": 401
  },
  "bu_login_err": null,
  "bu": {
    "/api/v1/vm/cockpit": 403,
    "/api/accounts": 401,
    "/api/v1/vm/bu/营销": 404,
    "/api/v1/vm/bu/不存在BU某某": 403,
    "/api/settings": 401
  },
  "admin": {
    "accounts": 200,
    "settings": 200,
    "vm_cockpit": 200
  }
}

## 期望解读
- noauth: accounts/cockpit/detail → 401
- overall: cockpit 200；accounts/detail/settings → 401
- bu: cockpit 403；accounts/settings 401；本BU vm 200或404(配置)；他BU 403
- admin: accounts/settings/vm 200